# ═══════════════════════════════════════
# DMT WEBSITE FRONTEND - ENVIRONMENT CONFIG
# ═══════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values

# ── BACKEND API URL ──
# Development: http://localhost:5000/api
# Production: https://your-backend-url.com/api
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

# ── DEPLOYMENT NOTES ──
# For Vercel deployment:
# 1. Update vercel.json with your actual backend URL
# 2. Or set VITE_API_URL in Vercel environment variables
# 3. Backend should be deployed separately (Render, Railway, etc.)

# ── LOCAL DEVELOPMENT ──
# 1. Start backend: cd backend && npm run dev
# 2. Serve frontend: Use Live Server or similar
# 3. Ensure backend is running on port 5000